org.corfudb.runtime.entries

Interface IStreamEntry

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<IStreamEntry>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DeferredTransaction, OpaqueDeferredTransaction, OptimisticTransaction, SimpleStreamEntry

    public interface IStreamEntry
extends Comparable<IStreamEntry>
    This interface represents the minimal functions that a stream entry must support. Created by mwei on 4/30/15.
